Step 5: Submit the Application
For Python:

spark-submit \
  --master spark://localhost:7077 \
  --executor-memory 1g \
  --total-executor-cores 2 \
  wordcount.py
Monitor the job execution in the Web UI at http://localhost:8080

Step 6: Test with Spark Shell
Launch the Spark shell connected to your cluster:

spark-shell --master spark://localhost:7077
Run a quick test in the shell:

